        <mxCell id="JOoKk0994VdbTXqO4fU7-1" parent="1" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;backgroundOutline=1;fontColor=#000000;darkOpacity=0.05;fillColor=#FFF9B2;strokeColor=none;fillStyle=solid;direction=west;gradientDirection=north;gradientColor=#FFF2A1;shadow=1;size=20;pointerEvents=1;" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;The logical topology shown above highlights key aspects of the configured network, including:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Device Hostnames&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Link Aggregation Connections using Fiber&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;IP address connections between devices&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;DHCP was configured on Juniper to ensure devices connected to the network could automatically receive an IP address&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;EIGRP zones highlighted in blue and red, where blue -&amp;gt; EIGRP 160, and red -&amp;gt; EIGRP 161.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;HSRP was configured through shared vlan gateways, where each IP corresponds to its associated vlan, respectively. The first row highlights gateways for ISR4331B,E, and Catalyst-B, while the second highlights gateways for ISR4331C and D.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;VLAN1&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| VLAN1601&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| VLAN1602&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| VLAN1603&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| VLAN1604&lt;br&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;192.168.1.2&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;|&amp;nbsp;192.168.16.2&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;| 192.168.26.2&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| 192.168.36.2&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| 192.168.46.2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(237, 237, 237));&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;192.168.11.1&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| 192.168.116.1&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| 192.168.126.1 &lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| 192.168.136.1 &lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;| 192.168.146.1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
